text: Ziyu "Sally" Zhang (born 10 December 1990) is an Australian table tennis player. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics as part of the Australian team in the women's team event. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Olympic table tennis players of Australia Category:Table tennis players at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Commonwealth Games medallists in table tennis Category:Commonwealth Games bronze medallists for Australia Category:Naturalised table tennis players Category:Table tennis players from Shijiazhuang Category:Table tennis players at the 2014 Commonwealth Games
title: Ziyu Zhang
